  <text>
    <body>
      <ab type="lido:objectWorkType">Still photograph</ab>
      <ab subtype="creation" type="lido:event">
        <date>1929</date>
      </ab>
      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The still from the feature film ‘Haiducii’ (Hajduks) shows a woman, a man and a mule or donkey. The couple are dressed in imaginative traditional costume and headgear. The man is looking at something on the right margin of the picture that cannot be identified. The woman is resting on his left arm with her eyes closed.</ab>
      <ab subtype="comment" type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The feature was directed by Horia Igirusanu and released in 1929.</ab>
